  <entry>
    <title>浅尝Paimon</title>
    <link href="/2023/07/18/pimon-230718/"/>
    <url>/2023/07/18/pimon-230718/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>  /* 设置整个页面的字体 */  html, body, .markdown-body {    font-family: STXihei, "华文细黑", "Microsoft YaHei", "微软雅黑";    font-size: 15px;  }</style><h1 id="01-总览"><a href="#01-总览" class="headerlink" title="01 总览"></a>01 总览</h1><p><strong>Streaming data lake platform with high-speed data ingestion, changelog tracking and efficient real-time analytics.</strong></p><p>Paimon 是一个具有 <code>高速数据摄取</code>、<code>变更日志跟踪</code> 和 <code>高效实时分析</code> 功能的 <strong>流数据湖平台</strong></p><p><a href="https://paimon.apache.org/">官网</a>、<a href="https://paimon.apache.org/docs/master">文档</a>、<a href="https://github.com/apache/incubator-paimon/">GitHub</a>、<a href="https://paimon.apache.org/community/how-to-contribute/">贡献指南</a>、<a href="https://paimon.apache.org/docs/master/project/roadmap/">Roadmap</a></p><div class="note note-info">            <p>Paimon核心支持Flink的数据读取，同时也支持Hive、Spark、Trino等计算引擎的读取</p>          </div><h2 id="1-1-架构"><a href="#1-1-架构" class="headerlink" title="1.1 架构"></a>1.1 架构</h2><p><img src="/img/paimon-architecture.png" alt="Paimon Architecture"></p><h2 id="1-2-基本概念-Basic-Concepts"><a href="#1-2-基本概念-Basic-Concepts" class="headerlink" title="1.2 基本概念 Basic Concepts"></a>1.2 基本概念 Basic Concepts</h2><ul><li><strong>Snapshot</strong><sup>快照</sup>: 快照是对表再某一瞬间的 <code>状态记录</code>，因此可以让用户进行Time-traveling(时间旅行)；</li><li><strong>Partition</strong><sup>分区</sup>: 和Hive类似，Paimon将数据按照分区来切分数据块；<br><span class="label label-primary">如果定义了主键，分区键必须是主键的子集。</span></li><li><strong>Bucket</strong><sup>桶</sup>: 对于 非分区表、已分区表 进行 <code>二次数据切分</code>。用户可以通过提供 <code>bucket-key</code> 选项来指定bucket列<br><span class="label label-primary">Bucket 是针对 <code>读/写的最小存储单元</code>，因此bucket的数量限制了最大的处理并行性。但是，这个数字不应该太大，因为它将导致大量小文件和低读取性能。<u>一般情况下，建议每个bucket中的数据大小为<strong>1GB</strong>左右</u></span></li><li><strong>Consistency Guarantees</strong><sup>一致性保证</sup>: 写表时，Paimon通过 <code>两阶段提交协议</code> 自动将一批记录提交出去（每次提交时最多产生两次snapshot）</li></ul><h1 id="02-核心"><a href="#02-核心" class="headerlink" title="02 核心"></a>02 核心</h1><h2 id="1-3-文件布局-File-Layouts"><a href="#1-3-文件布局-File-Layouts" class="headerlink" title="1.3 文件布局 File Layouts"></a>1.3 文件布局 File Layouts</h2><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-layout.png" alt="Paimon File Layout"></p><ol><li><strong>Snapshot Files</strong><sup>快照文件</sup>: 快照文件均存储在上图的 <code>snapshot</code> 文件夹中，这些文件是 JSON 格式的，其中包含了 <span class="label label-info">元数据信息</span> 和 <span class="label label-info">快照的变更记录列表</span></li><li><strong>Manifest Files</strong><sup>清单文件</sup>: 清单文件均存储在上图的 <code>manifest</code> 文件夹中， 每个 <code>manifest-list</code> 中由1个以上的 <code>manifest-file</code> 组成，每个 manifset-file 包含了 <span class="label label-info">LSM数据文件</span> 和 <span class="label label-info">changelog files</span></li><li><strong>Data Files</strong><sup>数据文件</sup>: 数据文件由 <code>partitions</code> 和 <code>buckets</code> 所组织，每个桶目录包含了一个 <span class="label label-info">LSM tree</span> 以及它的 <span class="label label-info">changelog files</span></li></ol><h3 id="1-3-1-简述-LSM-Trees"><a href="#1-3-1-简述-LSM-Trees" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1 简述 LSM Trees"></a>1.3.1 简述 LSM Trees</h3><p><img src="/img/lsm-sorted-run.png" alt="LSM"></p><p>LSM 树将文件以多个 <span class="label label-success">sorted runs</span><sup>序运行</sup> 组成。<code>sorted runs</code> 由多个 <code>data files</code> 组成，每个<code>sorted runs</code> 都是唯一的。</p><h4 id="查询操作"><a href="#查询操作" class="headerlink" title="查询操作"></a>查询操作</h4><p>不同的 <code>sorted runs</code> 中可能包含相同主键的 <code>data files</code>，所以 <span class="label label-danger">在查询LSM树的时候，必须按照用户指定的合并引擎规则搭配时间戳合并相同主键的sorted runs集合</span></p><h4 id="写入操作"><a href="#写入操作" class="headerlink" title="写入操作"></a>写入操作</h4><p>新纪录将首先在内存中缓冲，当缓冲区已满时，将对内存中的所有记录进行排序并刷写到磁盘中。</p><h4 id="合并操作"><a href="#合并操作" class="headerlink" title="合并操作"></a>合并操作</h4><p>当越来越多的数据写入LSM树，刷写出来的 <code>sorted runs</code> 将会堆积，为了处理因为大量 <code>sorted runs</code> 带来的查询性能低下(甚至是OOM情形)，Paimon使用了 <span class="label label-info">Compaction</span> 操作来合并小单位的 <code>sorted runs</code>。</p><p>类似于 Rocksdb 的 <em>universal compation</em><sup id="fnref:1" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="xxx">[1]</span></a></sup>，Paimon 的Compaction策略也是在”读”&#x2F;“写”之间进行性能的抉择，因为合并动作对于数据块来说是一个敏感的锁式操作，对于CPU和磁盘I&#x2F;O影响较大。</p><h2 id="1-4-文件操作-File-Operations"><a href="#1-4-文件操作-File-Operations" class="headerlink" title="1.4 文件操作 File Operations"></a>1.4 文件操作 File Operations</h2><h3 id="1-4-1-Flink集成Paimon"><a href="#1-4-1-Flink集成Paimon" class="headerlink" title="1.4.1 Flink集成Paimon"></a>1.4.1 Flink集成Paimon</h3><p>从 <a href="https://repository.apache.org/snapshots/org/apache/paimon/">Flink集成jar包</a> 路径下载对应flink版本的官方jar包(1.14&#x2F;1.15&#x2F;1.16&#x2F;1.17)，拷贝到 <code>$FLINK_HOME/lib/</code> 下(按需改名)</p><div class="note note-info">            <p>此处编者使用了 <code>paimon-flink-1.17-0.5.jar</code> 作为三方包</p>          </div><p>如果是 <em>flink on hadoop</em> 集成环境，还需进行如下操作之一：</p><ul><li>环境变量注入 <code>$HADOOP_CLASSPATH</code> <span class="label label-info">编者配置了但不使用HDFS等分布式存储</span></li><li>引入三方shaded包(flink-shaded-hadoop-2-uber-*.jar)至 <code>$FLINK_HOME/lib/</code> 中</li></ul><p>修改flink的TM工作槽为2，从而方便后续的 <em>多任务功能</em> 校验</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">taskmanager.numberOfTaskSlots:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过 sql-client.sh 进行简单的 FlinkSQL 操作 Paimon 表验证：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">bigdata$ sh <span class="hljs-variable">$FLINK_HOME</span>/bin/sql-client.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-4-2-操作速览"><a href="#1-4-2-操作速览" class="headerlink" title="1.4.2 操作速览"></a>1.4.2 操作速览</h3><h4 id="创建Catalog"><a href="#创建Catalog" class="headerlink" title="创建Catalog"></a>创建Catalog</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-comment">-- warehouse的路径在分布式路径中使用专有协议，如 HDFS 或 OSS 等</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> CATALOG my_catalog <span class="hljs-keyword">WITH</span> (<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;type&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;paimon&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;warehouse&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;file:/tmp/paimon&#x27;</span><br>);<br><br>USE CATALOG my_catalog;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="创建表"><a href="#创建表" class="headerlink" title="创建表"></a>创建表</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> T (<br>  id <span class="hljs-type">BIGINT</span>,<br>  a <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>  b STRING,<br>  dt STRING COMMENT <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;timestamp string in format yyyyMMdd&#x27;</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY(id, dt) <span class="hljs-keyword">NOT</span> ENFORCED<br>) PARTITIONED <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> (dt);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>操作以后可以本地查看到表结构：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">bigdata$ <span class="hljs-built_in">pwd</span><br>/tmp/paimon<br>bigdata$ tree<br>.<br>└── default.db<br>    └── T<br>        └── schema<br>            └── schema-0<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="插入单条数据"><a href="#插入单条数据" class="headerlink" title="插入单条数据"></a>插入单条数据</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10001</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00001&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230501&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时可以进入 <code>/tmp/paimon/default.db/T/</code> 查看文件层次：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">bigdata$ tree<br>.<br>├── dt=20230501<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-464db983-ff5e-47cc-9fcc-2ec7d7c89d37-0.orc<br>├── manifest<br>│   ├── manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0<br>│   └── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1<br>├── schema<br>│   └── schema-0<br>└── snapshot<br>    ├── EARLIEST<br>    ├── LATEST<br>    └── snapshot-1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-0.png" alt="首次快照插入流程"></p><p>接下来我们逐一分析 <span class="label label-danger">重点文件</span>：</p><h5 id="snapshot-1"><a href="#snapshot-1" class="headerlink" title="snapshot-1"></a>snapshot-1</h5><p>包含了快照的 <em>元数据信息</em></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;version&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;id&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;schemaId&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;baseManifestList&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;deltaManifestList&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;changelogManifestList&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commitUser&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;32d30dbe-ef3d-46ba-959b-267917cb538d&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commitIdentifier&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">9223372036854775807</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commitKind&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;APPEND&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;timeMillis&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1690157348811</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;logOffsets&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;totalRecordCount&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;deltaRecordCount&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;changelogRecordCount&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;watermark&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">-9223372036854775808</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>它描述了两个核心概念：<span class="label label-info">baseManifestList</span> 和 <span class="label label-info">deltaManifestList</span>；</p><ul><li><strong>baseManifestList</strong>：基础清单列表，有关deltaManifestList的每次更改都将应用于baseManifestList；<blockquote><p>对应到上面的流程图中就是 <em>manifest-list-1-base</em></p></blockquote></li><li><strong>deltaManifestList</strong>：每次操作的增量清单列表。（附属 <code>manifest file</code> 的生成）<blockquote><p>对应到上面的流程图中就是 <em>manifest-list-1-delta</em> 和 <em>manifest-1-0</em></p></blockquote></li></ul><div class="note note-info">            <p>首次提交会产生1个 <code>manifest file</code> 和2个 <code>manifest lists</code></p>          </div><h5 id="manifest-manifest-list"><a href="#manifest-manifest-list" class="headerlink" title="manifest &amp; manifest-list"></a>manifest &amp; manifest-list</h5><p>看完核心概念再来看编者 <code>manifest</code>文件夹下 的实际文件：</p><ul><li>manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0：存储并描述了数据文件块在快照中信息；</li><li>manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0：实际上是空的</li><li>manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1：包含了对数据文件执行操作的清单条目列表</li></ul><h4 id="插入批量数据"><a href="#插入批量数据" class="headerlink" title="插入批量数据"></a>插入批量数据</h4><p>FlinkSQL执行：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> <br>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10002</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00002&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230502&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10003</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00003&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230503&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">4</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10004</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00004&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230504&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10005</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00005&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230505&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">6</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10006</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00006&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230506&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">7</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10007</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00007&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230507&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">8</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10008</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00008&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230508&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">9</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10009</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00009&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230509&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10010</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00010&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230510&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入 <code>/tmp/paimon/default.db/T/</code> 查看文件层次：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">bigdata$ tree<br>.<br>├── dt=20230501<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-464db983-ff5e-47cc-9fcc-2ec7d7c89d37-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230502<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-cc196bd5-f86c-426f-a6af-eff0d5d394f5-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230503<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-0dbb8fab-01cb-43fa-bd37-fa9c9d96ceff-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230504<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-e6973ba6-c00f-42ed-8369-60889f8c0ba2-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230505<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-8242dd5d-33cd-46a7-97e3-99a3968d6ed1-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230506<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-d7ff1a46-02e8-4713-a53d-89b357c6a5bb-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230507<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-dadac0a6-5503-494e-8fdc-c9d7dcfee79a-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230508<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-8e123e3c-90e8-49e4-9d08-6c222e41ba0d-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230509<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-ac3be585-7b8a-4b3e-b756-738f69d0ad0b-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230510<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-835009a9-863a-4301-bce3-d94ec7ba13b0-0.orc<br>├── manifest<br>│   ├── manifest-2526d0f2-81ff-429b-af9a-8707d050c17c-0<br>│   ├── manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1<br>│   ├── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-0<br>│   └── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-1<br>├── schema<br>│   └── schema-0<br>└── snapshot<br>    ├── EARLIEST<br>    ├── LATEST<br>    ├── snapshot-1<br>    └── snapshot-2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-1.png" alt="二次(批量)快照插入流程"></p><p>可以看到，第一次快照动作产生的 <code>baseManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-base) 和 <code>deltaManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-delta) 已经不再被最新的快照 <code>snapshot-2</code> 所描述，新产生的 <code>baseManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>2</strong>-base) 是合并了 <code>snapshot-1</code> 中增量清单列表和基础清单列表的结果（manifest-list-<strong>2</strong>-base &#x3D;&gt; manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-base + manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-delta）</p><p>同时由 <code>snapshot-2</code> 产生的 <code>deltaManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>2</strong>-delta) 将用于描述本次批量插入的从 20230502分区 ~ 20230510分区 的数据增量信息。</p><div class="note note-info">            <p>不难猜出，对于某张表每次的快照插入操作，都会将上一次的 <code>deltaManifestList</code> 和 <code>baseManifestList</code> 按照某种合并策略进行 <strong>Compaction</strong></p>          </div><h4 id="删除数据"><a href="#删除数据" class="headerlink" title="删除数据"></a>删除数据</h4><h4 id="合并表"><a href="#合并表" class="headerlink" title="合并表"></a>合并表</h4><h4 id="修改表"><a href="#修改表" class="headerlink" title="修改表"></a>修改表</h4><h4 id="过期快照"><a href="#过期快照" class="headerlink" title="过期快照"></a>过期快照</h4><h4 id="Flink流写"><a href="#Flink流写" class="headerlink" title="Flink流写"></a>Flink流写</h4><h2 id="1-5-主键表-Primary-Key-Table"><a href="#1-5-主键表-Primary-Key-Table" class="headerlink" title="1.5 主键表 Primary Key Table"></a>1.5 主键表 Primary Key Table</h2><h2 id="1-6-仅追加表-Append-Only-Table"><a href="#1-6-仅追加表-Append-Only-Table" class="headerlink" title="1.6 仅追加表 Append Only Table"></a>1.6 仅追加表 Append Only Table</h2><h2 id="1-7-外部日志系统-External-Log-Systems"><a href="#1-7-外部日志系统-External-Log-Systems" class="headerlink" title="1.7 外部日志系统 External Log Systems"></a>1.7 外部日志系统 External Log Systems</h2><h1 id="03-引擎-Engines"><a href="#03-引擎-Engines" class="headerlink" title="03 引擎 Engines"></a>03 引擎 Engines</h1><h1 id="04-文件系统-Filesystems"><a href="#04-文件系统-Filesystems" class="headerlink" title="04 文件系统 Filesystems"></a>04 文件系统 Filesystems</h1><h1 id="05-用法指导-How-to"><a href="#05-用法指导-How-to" class="headerlink" title="05 用法指导 How to"></a>05 用法指导 How to</h1><h1 id="06-运维调优-Maintenance"><a href="#06-运维调优-Maintenance" class="headerlink" title="06 运维调优 Maintenance"></a>06 运维调优 Maintenance</h1><h1 id="07-三方调用-API"><a href="#07-三方调用-API" class="headerlink" title="07 三方调用 API"></a>07 三方调用 API</h1><h1 id="08-引用说明"><a href="#08-引用说明" class="headerlink" title="08 引用说明"></a>08 引用说明</h1><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>xxx<a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
