    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="01-Spark"><a href="#01-Spark" class="headerlink" title="01 Spark"></a>01 Spark</h2><h3 id="1-1-Local模式"><a href="#1-1-Local模式" class="headerlink" title="1.1 Local模式"></a>1.1 Local模式</h3><ol><li>解压tar包；</li><li>运行官方Pi案例： <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; bin/spark-submit \<br>--class org.apache.spark.examples.SparkPi \<br>--master <span class="hljs-built_in">local</span>[2] \<br>./examples/jars/spark-examples_2.12-3.0.0.jar \<br>10<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>运行官方WordCount案例： <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; bin/spark-shell<br>...<br>scala&gt; sc.textFile(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/home/bigdata/modules/spark-3.2.4/tmp_data/input.txt&quot;</span>).flatMap(_.<span class="hljs-built_in">split</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>)).map((_,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)).reduceByKey(_+_).collect<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="1-2-Standalone模式"><a href="#1-2-Standalone模式" class="headerlink" title="1.2 Standalone模式"></a>1.2 Standalone模式</h3><p>由Spark使用自身的资源调动引擎管理 Master 和 Worker</p><blockquote><p>为方便测试仅在单节点上部署单节点伪集群模式(Master和Worker均在一台机器)</p></blockquote><p>直接启动命令：<code>./sbin/start-all.sh</code><br>网页查看：<a href="http://localhost:8080/">http://localhost:8080</a><br>运行官方Pi案例：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; bin/spark-submit \<br>--class org.apache.spark.examples.SparkPi \<br>--master spark://locahost:7077 \<br>./examples/jars/spark-examples_2.12-3.2.4.jar \<br>10<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-2-1-提交参数进阶"><a href="#1-2-1-提交参数进阶" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1 提交参数进阶"></a>1.2.1 提交参数进阶</h4><ul><li>–<strong>executor-memory</strong>: 指定Executor内存</li><li>–<strong>total-executor-cores</strong>: 指定Executor核数</li><li>–<strong>deploy-mode</strong>：指定运行模式：<ul><li><em>client</em>：Driver程序在本地运行</li><li><em>cluster</em>：Driver程序在集群中运行</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="1-3-Yarn模式"><a href="#1-3-Yarn模式" class="headerlink" title="1.3 Yarn模式"></a>1.3 Yarn模式</h3><p>启动好 HDFS 和 Yarn 后，执行Pi案例：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; bin/spark-submit \<br>--class org.apache.spark.examples.SparkPi \<br>--master yarn \<br>./examples/jars/spark-examples_2.12-3.2.4.jar \<br>10<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-3-1-集成Spark的historyServer"><a href="#1-3-1-集成Spark的historyServer" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1 集成Spark的historyServer"></a>1.3.1 集成Spark的historyServer</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">mv</span> spark-defaults.conf.template spark-defaults.conf<br><br>&gt; vi spark-defaults.conf<br>spark.eventLog.enabled<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>spark.eventLog.<span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span>hdfs://node-001:8020/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;directory&#125;</span><br>spark.yarn.historyServer.address=node-001:18080<br>spark.history.ui.port=18080<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 参数1含义：WEBUI访问的端口号为18080</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 参数2含义：指定历史服务器日志存储路径</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 参数3含义：指定保存Application历史记录的个数，如果超过这个值，旧的应用程序信息将被删除，这个是内存中的应用数，而不是页面上显示的应用数</span><br>&gt; vi spark-env.sh<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> SPARK_HISTORY_OPTS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">-Dspark.history.ui.port=18080 </span><br><span class="hljs-string">-Dspark.history.fs.logDirectory=hdfs://node-001:8020/<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;directory&#125;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-string">-Dspark.history.retainedApplications=30&quot;</span><br><br>./sbin/spark-start-hitory-server.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此，spark的history服务就集成到了hadoop中，访问 <a href="http://node-001:18080/">http://node-001:18080</a> 可以查看历时任务，同时可从yarn管理页面跳转。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; bin/spark-submit \<br>--class org.apache.spark.examples.SparkPi \<br>--master yarn \<br>./examples/jars/spark-examples_2.12-3.2.4.jar \<br>10<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-2-运行模式"><a href="#1-3-2-运行模式" class="headerlink" title="1.3.2 运行模式"></a>1.3.2 运行模式</h3><ol><li><strong>yarn-client</strong>(默认)：Driver程序运行在客户端，适用于交互、调试，希望立即看到app的输出</li><li><strong>yarn-cluster</strong>：Driver程序运行在由ResourceManager启动的APPMaster适用于生产环境</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">&gt; bin/spark-submit --deploy-mode client/cluster ...<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
